   How to Get Help
       Fill out a Citizen Service Request Form
       Contacts:
     * Neighborhood Service Coordinators
     * Neighborhood Planning Coordinators
     * Neighborhood Stabilization Officers
     * Solid Waste Education & Enforcement Program (SWEEP) Contacts
     * Street and Alley Cleaning Contacts
     * Rat Abatement (Vector Control) Contacts
     * Solid Waste Collection Contacts
     * Environmental Crime Unit
     * Rapid Response Teams
     * Health, Rodent, and Sanitation Contacts

       Other help:
     * Abandoned Vehicles
     * Get Help with a Neighborhood Cleanup
     * How to get Bulk Trash collected
     * How to obtain a new Supercan
     * How to obtain a Recycle Container
     * Dead Animal Removal
     * Public Space Regulations (General, Commercial, Residential,
       Posters)
     * Rodent Control
     * Trash Container Regulations
